bio.original:
DANC SOUND aka Danny Clarke is a bass producer/DJ from the United Kingdom.
                            Influenced by the heavy bass sounds of Mad Decent / OWSLA artists,
                            DANC’s ability to seamlessly mix break, house,dubstep and electro
                            into hard hitting club-shakers has become a trademark of the cliche
                            DANC x SOUND.
